<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.14">
<l>aṉṉa naṭaimaṭa vāycci vayiṟaṭit tañcava ruvarai pōla</l>
<l>maṉṉu karuṅkaḷiṟ ṟāruyir vavviya maintaṉai māka ṭalcūḻ</l>
<l>kaṉṉinaṉ māmatiḷ maṅkaiyar kāvalaṉ kāmaru cīrkkali kaṉṟi</l>
<l>yiṉṉicai mālaika ḷīrēḻum vallavark kētumi ṭaril laiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master the two-times-seven [verses]</l>
<l rend="indent">of the sweet musical garlands</l>
<l>By Kalikaṉṟi of desired esteem, protector of those of Maṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with fine, great, impenetrable walls surrounded by the vast sea,</l>
<l>About the boy who snatched the dear life of a dark elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">solid as a huge mountain,</l>
<l>As the simple herdess with a swan’s gait panicked, beating her belly,</l>
<l rend="indent">there will not be any sorrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
